StormHarbour Hires Citigroup’s Paulo Gray as a Managing Director

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-09-28T11:59:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/stormharbour-hires-citigroup-s-paulo-gray-as-a-managing-director.html
StormHarbour, a financial advisory
company, hired Paulo Gray, former head of markets for  Portugal 
at  Citigroup Inc. (C) , as a principal and managing director.  Gray will be responsible for the company’s client
relationships and coverage in Portugal and  Spain , the company
said today in an e-mailed statement.  “Portugal and the broader Iberian region offer compelling
growth opportunities to the firm and its global client base,”
StormHarbour said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anabela Reis in Lisbon at 
 areis1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  